@getpradeep9 it basically says that the language doesn't have something like:
```
public someMethod() {
  // ...
}

private someOtherMethod {
  // ...
}
```

In order to make something visible outside, you'll have to use a capital letter, as in: 
```
SomeMethod() {
 // ...
 // SomeMethod can be seen from outside
}

someOtherMethod {
 // this one can't, it doesn't begin with a capital letter
}
```
